    <div class="collapsible-header">Does the scope have a measurement function?</div>
    <div class="collapsible-body"><p>No. While some very high-end Borescopes offer a measurement function, most Borescope users have often found the function unnecessary and unreliable. As a result, we at SPI Borescopes decided to make the best possible scope, with only the most necessary features, at incredibly affordable prices.</p></div>
  </li>
  <li>
    <div class="collapsible-header">How does SPI Borescopes compare with less expensive scopes on the market?</div>
    <div class="collapsible-body"><p>There are few low-end Borescopes on the market with price points between $200 and $500.  These are typically very simple Borescopes.  They do not offer articulation and often have very poor picture quality.  We suggest you try one and compare.  For a little more money our scopes provide significantly higher quality and features.</p></div>
  </li>
