    <div class="collapsible-body"><p>The Borescope market has traditionally been controlled by a handful of giant medical device and manufacturing companies. These companies used technology originally developed for the medical market and slightly modified this technology for the industrial inspection industry.
While this process has led to innovative technologies, it is also the cause of the hyper -inflated pricing common to this industry. Over the last few years we have seen more and more mid-level firms entering the market, taking the average Articulating Borescope prices down from the 20K-50K price range to the low 10’s of thousands. SPI Borescopes now offers a better solution. We bring you all the high-end technology you need, but at a fraction of the price other new mid-level firms are offering. Give us a call and learn more about our extremely competitive prices.</p>
  </li>
